OL,3,CDerbyshire Police's driver crackdown
OL,4,Csees 50% drop in fatal or serious
OL,5,Ccrashes
OL,7,FA month long crack-down on fatal four
OL,8,Froad offences has led to a significant
OL,9,Fdrop in the number of fatal or serious
OL,10,Fcollisions.
OL,12,FDerbyshire Police ran 'Op Rapidity'
OL,13,Fthroughout March, targeting a
OL,14,Fdifferent one of the fatal four each
OL,15,Fweek.
OL,17,FThey are drink and drug driving,
OL,18,Fspeeding, using a mobile phone whilst
OL,19,Fdriving and not wearing a seatbelt.
