OL,3,CDerbyshire Police's driver crackdown
OL,4,Csees 50% drop in fatal or serious
OL,5,Ccrashes
OL,7,FThe force says that whilst they are
OL,8,Fpleased that the number of serious
OL,9,Fcollisions fell, the number of
OL,10,Foffences identified shows that there
OL,11,Fis 'still work to do.'
OL,13,FInspector Greg Hunt of the Roads
OL,14,FPolicing Team said, "Many of the fatal
OL,15,For serious collisions we attend have
OL,16,Finvolved at least one of the fatal
OL,17,Ffour offences so we are committed to
OL,18,Feducating motorists on the dangers of
OL,19,Fthese actions."
