OL,3,CDerbyshire Police's driver crackdown
OL,4,Csees 50% drop in fatal or serious
OL,5,Ccrashes
OL,7,F"Initiatives such as Op Rapidity are a
OL,8,Fvital part of our work to keep
OL,9,Feveryone who uses Derbyshire's roads
OL,10,Fsafe."
OL,12,F"It was pleasing to see such a large
OL,13,Fdecrease in the number of killed or
OL,14,Fseriously injured collisions during Op
OL,15,FRapidity but the numbers of people
OL,16,Ffound to be committing offences and
OL,17,Fdealt with during the initiative shows
OL,18,Fthere is still some work to do."
